project_id.description: Your project ID number. See the docs for more information on how to obtain this: https://help.mixpanel.com/hc/en-us/articles/115004490503-Project-Settings#project-id

project_timezone.description: Time zone in which integer date times are stored. The project timezone may be found in the project settings in the Mixpanel console: https://help.mixpanel.com/hc/en-us/articles/115004547203-Manage-Timezones-for-Projects-in-Mixpanel
